# AUC — source of truth

All work for this pack must align with [AUC Venture Lab Women Innovation Fellowship 2026](https://opportunitiesforyouth.org/2026/07/16/auc-venture-lab-women-innovation-fellowship-empowering-women-entrepreneurs-in-egypt-and-beyond/). That page wins on eligibility, theme, format, and deadlines.

Also follow `.cursor/rules/documents.mdc` and `.cursor/rules/folder_structure.mdc`.

## Call angle

Women entrepreneurship fellowship in Cairo (1 Sep–31 Oct 2026). HealthTech / AI fit for FCHIP. Deadline **25 July 2026**. Frame leadership training + ecosystem access returning to FairBanks community health.

## Mandatory checks

1. Women innovator narrative; HealthTech among covered industries; Egypt programme with cross-regional exposure.
2. Clear win-win: fellow + AUC V-Lab + FairBanks communities.
3. Root in FairBanks cascade; FCHIP as a FairBanks component — intelligence layer — not software-only claims.
4. Simple human language. Only approved slogan: **Your health, our mission.**
5. Re-check official page before finalising.

