## Cover / branding

- **PowerPoint (`auc_ppt.pptx`):** Elegant by default — balanced type beside photos, real pictures from `assets/`, clean design, light purposeful animations. Follow `.cursor/rules/documents.mdc`.
- Programme name, FairBanks/FCHIP framing, document title, **Your health, our mission.**, hero image.
- **Do not** put an application-details summary table on the first page unless the live call requires it.
